title: ACC 53 Grade Cement
desc: , , ACC 53 Grade Cement, , ACC OPC 53 grade cement is an ordinary portland cement which surpasses the requirements of IS: 12269-53 grade. It is produced from high quality clinker ground with high purity gypsum.\xa0ACC 53 grade OPC cement provides high strength and durability to structures because of its optimum particle size distribution, superior crystalline structure and balanced phase composition.\xa0It is available in specially designed 50 kg bags., ,

title: ACC 43 Grade Cement
desc: , , ACC 43 Grade Cement, , ACC OPC 43 Grade Cement is the most commonly used cement in all construction projects including plain and reinforced cement concrete, brick and stone masonry, floors and plastering. It is also used in the finishing of all types of buildings, bridges, culverts, roads, water retaining structures, etc.\xa0ACC Cement surpasses BIS Specifications (IS 8112-1989 for 43 grade OPC) on compressive strength levels.\xa0ACC Cement is marketed in specially designed 50 kg bags., ,

title: ACC PPC Cement
desc: , , ACC PPC Cement, , ACC PPC Grade Cement is an Portland Pozzolana Cement. It is produced from high quality clinker ground with high purity gypsum.\xa0ACC PPC Cement has ingredients which react with calcium hydroxide to form CSH gel, to provide additional strength, which actually makes the concrete grow in strength over the years. It also produces less heat of hydration and offers greater resistance to the attack of aggressive waters than normal Portland cement.\xa0ACC PPC Grade Cement provides high strength and durability to structures because of its optimum particle size distribution, superior crystalline structure and balanced phase composition.\xa0It is available in specially designed 50 kg bags., ,

title: Anjani 53 Grade Cement
desc: , , Anjani 53 Grade Cement, , Anjani 53 Grade Cement is the most commonly used cement in all construction projects including plain and reinforced cement concrete, brick and stone masonry, floors and plastering. It is also used in the finishing of all types of buildings, bridges, culverts, roads, water retaining structures, etc.\xa0Anjani Cement is marketed in specially designed 50 kg bags., ,

title: Bharathi 53 Grade Cement
desc: , Bharathi 53 Grade Cement, , Bharathi Cement Corporation Private Limited is a producer of superior quality cement setting new standards in construction and is a subsidiary of Vicat Group in India.\xa0Bharathi 53 Grade OPC is an Ordinary Portland Cement which surpasses the requirements set by IS12269-1987 Grade. It is produced by inter grinding of high grade clinker (with high C3S content) and right quality gypsum in predetermined proportions.\xa0Bharathi OPC 53 Grade cement is recognized for its high early strength and excellent ultimate strength because of its optimum particle size distribution, superior crystalline structure and balanced phase composition and hence widely used and suitable for speedy construction, durable concrete and economic concrete mix designs.\xa0Bharathi 53 Grade Cement is known for low percentages of alkalies, chlorides, magnesia and free lime. It is durable concrete with high strength.,

Bharathi PPC Cement
desc: , Bharathi PPC Cement, , Bharathi Portland pozzolana (PPC) cement is a premium composite cement manufactured by inter grinding of high quality clinker, carefully selected High reactive Silica (HRS) obtained from electrostatic precipitators with right quality gypsum.\xa0This unique, value-added product has hydraulic binding properties not found in ordinary cements. This product has various advantages compared to ordinary Portland cement as it has a low heat of hydration, resistance to sulphate attack and chloride attack. It us resistant to alkali silica reaction and is known for reduction in water demand. Due to high fineness of cement it reduces bleeding. \xa0The pore refinement leads to improved density of concrete.,

title: Bharathi 43 Grade Cement
desc: , , Bharathi 43 Grade Cement, , Bharathi Cement Corporation Private Limited is a producer of superior quality cement setting new standards in construction and is a subsidiary of Vicat Group in India.\xa0Bharathi Cement\u2019s ultra modern manufacturing plant has a production capacity of over 5 Million Tonnes per annum.\xa0Bharathi OPC 43 Grade Cement is used in all construction projects including plain and reinforced cement concrete, brick and stone masonry, floors and plastering. It is also used in all types of residential and commercial complexes, bridges, culverts, roads, water retaining structures, as well as for construction of highways and runways etc., ,

Due to its inherent characteristics, PPC aids in creating corrosion resistant concrete that is far superior to concrete made with OPC.\xa0Priya PPC cement is a product of Rain Cements Limited (RCL\x80\x9d) which is a leading producer of 3.12 million tons per annum of cement in South India since 1986. desc: , Coromandel PPC Cement, , Coromandel Super Power is the premium blended cements from THE INDIA CEMENTS LIMITED. It is produced by intergrinding of PPC clinker along with gypsum and mineral admixtures. Dedicated to the end user after passing through stringent tests at their\xa0R&D laboratory, it ensures durable structures that lasts for generations. Coromandel cement ensures increase in strength as the time passes. It is known to be a high durable concrete \xa0as it protects from corrosion, coastal attack and extreme temperature. It is an ideal cement for resisting aggressive environments like chemical, chloride and sulphate attack. It is best suited for high performance concrete. Its high fineness is suited for plastering and finishing works. Known for its low heat of hydration, it is \xa0ideal for mass concrete pours and machine foundations. \xa0The coromandel PPC is equivalent to 53 grade cement.,

It is ideal\xa0for residential , commercial and all multi-storey buildings,\xa0RCC Works, hollow blocks, PCC solid, spun pipes, poles and all industrial application & culverts, bridges, dams, flyovers and others. Key feature of wire cut brick are:, , , Solid construction, , Durable, , Fine finish, , , Size of Red Clay Bricks is\xa09\u2033 X 4\u2033 X 3\u2033,
